

get ajax data

load thumbnail urls with AJAX
	get ajax data from xml data file
	parse ajax data
	append data to a global list of thumbnails
	display thumbnails into column layout
	add event listeners to thumbnails

iterateImages by iterator
	get current image index
	increment by iterator modulo list length
	load and display new image
	
thumbnail click
	get image url from selected thumbnail
	change suffix from thumbnail to full image
	open image box
	load image into box

close button click
	hide imagebox

left arrow key
	if imagebox open
		iterate images backwards 1

right arryow key
	if imagebox open
		itarete images forwards 1

escape key
	if imagebox open
		close imagebox

previous button click
	iterate images backwards 1

next button click
	iterate images forwards 1

open image
	set imagebox source to image
	fade new image in

open imagebox
	fade imagebox in
	lock scrolling

close imagebox
	fade imagebox out
	unlock scrolling